name: Eagle Speedmapping Session 8 - Memesis
description: The eighth Eagle Speedmapping Sessions' goal was to make maps within a 2 (in practice 3) hour limit. Nine maps were completed, and the themes were: - Birthday cake (for NaZa :P) - No keys - No more than 10 Tags Plus a bonus theme for the chaps who showed up for the final round: - a la Downtown (city-like)
